URL Shortener: A program that takes long URLs and converts them into shorter ones that users can easily remember 1.
Content Aggregator: A program that scrapes content from multiple websites and aggregates them into one place. You can use this to create a news aggregator or a job board 1.
Data Analysis: Analyze data using Python libraries like Pandas, NumPy, and Matplotlib. You can use this to analyze data from a CSV file or a database 2.
